messages.msgSnippet: I absolutely adore the OTSBH sling. So much so that I used to sell them. I also made my own nursing wear as part of the business. I first got a NOJO sling when
messages.messageBody:
I absolutely adore the OTSBH sling. So much so that I used to sell
them. I also made my own nursing wear as part of the business. I
first got a NOJO sling when my 2nd was born but it was too big and I
didn't do it up properly and I didn't know how to use it either.
I gave it away.
I next saw a LLLleader with an OTSBH at a meeting w/ #3. I was so
impressed!
I've been a faithful sling user ever since. I have one in the car and
(actually) 2 in the house! dh won't let me have more than 3 ;) so
when I wanted another fabric as a distributor, I had to sell one of
the other ones so I could buy a new one.

I don't use it as much around the house now as I did w/ #3 and 4 but
I still have to know where my sling is at all times. I LOVE the sling!
I don't sell anymore but not because I don't love it!


Venita, mom to katie 9, jon 8, rachel 5, jessica 3 and peter 1
http://www.geocities.com/mommycash/index.html code: 13114
